    "body": "@fjl I believe this issue can be safely closed since this PR: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/26310.\r\n`FeedOf` comes with this feature built-in.\r\n\r\n```go\r\ntype Message interface{ Value() int }\r\ntype SomeMessage struct{ v int }\r\n\r\nfunc (m SomeMessage) Value() int {\r\n\treturn m.v\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunc TestFeedOfInterface(t *testing.T) {\r\n\tfeed := FeedOf[Message]{}\r\n\tch := make(chan Message)\r\n\tfeed.Subscribe(ch)\r\n\r\n\tgo func() {\r\n\t\tif n := feed.Send(SomeMessage{1}); n != 1 {\r\n\t\t\tt.Error(\"failed to send SomeMessage{1}\")\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t}()\r\n\r\n\tmsg, ok := (<-ch).(SomeMessage)\r\n\tif !ok {\r\n\t\tt.Error(\"did not receive SomeMessage type\")\r\n\t}\r\n\tif msg != (SomeMessage{1}) {\r\n\t\tt.Error(\"did not receive SomeMessage{1}\")\r\n\t}\r\n}\r\n```",
